txt.en: A powerful host of Orcs makes camp within Zhar Dushgoi.\n\nYou should seek out one of the captains in Zhar Dushgoi and defeat him.
Defeat one of Gothmog's captains in Zhar Dushgoi
'You did very well, my friend! Those Orcs are sure to miss that captain. Please accept my thanks.'

'East of here lies Zhar Dushgoi, an Orc encampment that has proven quite a thorn in our side already. Within that camp, several captains serve to keep their subordinates in line. Would you venture into the area and defeat one of the captains? I do not care which! Any of them will do!'
Return to Thornaran and inform him that you defeated an Orc captain in Zhar Dushgoi.
Zhar Dushgoi lies east of Barad Angarth in the outer ring of Minas Morgul. Thornaran asked you to seek out and defeat its Orc captains.
